{
  "stem": "18486.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 129,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had [NON-ENGLISH] Mussert, who was the head of the-- of the National Socialistic Party.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mussert.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "M-U-S-S-E-R-T.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 131,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was not a Jewish community.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 131,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 132,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Jewish who lived there, well, they all were scared of Mussert, of course.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we hid them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 134,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We hid the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 135,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 135,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was as soon as Hitler started to enter-- in Holland.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 136,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 136,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Prior to that, we didn't have to protect anybody, with nothing happened to them yet.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 137,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 137,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 138,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But Mussert started a little after Hitler in-- in-- had started in Germany, of course.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 138,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then when Germany came to-- how you say-- occupied Holland, then Mussert was there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 138,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But he was under the thumb of Hitler.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 138,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 139,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 140,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In 1939 and earlier, '38, with Kristallnacht--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 141,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 142,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--when there were all these laws that went into effect in Germany--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 143,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 144,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--Jews began to migrate to--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 145,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To Holland.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 146,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 147,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 148,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they found jobs and they were-- people were very nice to them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 148,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They welcomed them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 148,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, they didn't ask them to come, but when they came and had to flee-- there were, of course-- there were also people in Holland who resented it.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 148,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the majority of the Dutch people were very anti-Hitler-- the vast majority-- and so the helped the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 149,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Beg your pardon?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 150,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I couldn't-- they talked about it, and the wrote in the paper about it, you know, and things like that.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 150,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But for-- they didn't attack them, or they didn't do anything to them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 150,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they were just resentful, they didn't like it that so many Jewish people came to Holland.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 150,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But they couldn't do anything about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 150,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because in general, the Dutch people agreed fully to help.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 151,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, sure.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 152,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I-- I don't remember that well.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 152,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was in 1940.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
